25:16.641 --> 25:17.983
In fact, I would testify.

25:18.023 --> 25:23.408
His mother and dad started coming to our church six months before he was diagnosed with leukemia.

25:25.070 --> 25:30.256
And they wouldn't mind me telling you this, because they testified repeatedly to it.

25:30.276 --> 25:35.922
They said, Pastor John, we would have gone insane.

25:36.706 --> 25:38.308
This is halfway through the treatments.

25:38.969 --> 25:39.930
We've gone insane.

25:41.072 --> 25:46.639
We're at naught for the sovereignty of God that we've heard proclaimed week after week.

25:50.063 --> 25:55.009
Henry Martin, the missionary who died at age, what, 30 or 29?

25:55.230 --> 26:01.097
If God has worked for me to do, I cannot die.

26:02.139 --> 26:04.882
You are immortal until your work is done.

26:05.698 --> 26:23.167
Christians ought to be the freest most risk-taking most radical people in the world Don't yield to the spirit of the age brothers take up whatever Sacrifices are necessary and whatever suffering is necessary.

26:23.207 --> 26:32.242
We'll talk about that more later And don't be afraid of controversy be courageous

26:34.210 --> 26:44.565
Thank you for listening to this episode of Light and Truth, where we are committed to providing God-centered preaching to help you see Christ clearly, treasure Him truly.

26:45.166 --> 26:46.628
I'm your host, Dan Kruver.

26:47.469 --> 27:01.209
On our next episode, Jumpiper continues our eight-part series, Living and Dying for the Glory of Christ, with a message titled, Why the Word Must Stand at the Center of Worship.

27:01.229 --> 27:02.130
I hope you'll join us.

27:02.594 --> 27:06.258
For more resources, visit desiringgod.org.

